title: Bucs and Cowboys thriller, Brady and Prescott, NFL Week 1 Previews, Aaron Jones, and Nate Burleson
itunes:title: Bucs and Cowboys thriller, Brady and Prescott, NFL Week 1 Previews, Aaron Jones, and Nate Burleson
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Michael Robinson, Peter Schrager and Kyle Brandt welcome the NFL season with Tom Brady and the Buccaneers winning over Dak Prescott and the Cowboys. We preview the rest of Week 1 and welcome Packers' RB Aaron Jones to the show. Nate Burleson drops by with his thoughts on the Bucs win.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
